Android App.ML Kit OCR -> Backend Server.Django REST Framework.API Endpoints: HTTP/JSON via adb reverse
Android App.Retrofit -> Backend Server.Django REST Framework.API Endpoints: HTTP/JSON via adb reverse
Backend Server.Django REST Framework.Database Models -> Database: Read/Write (psycopg)
Backend Server.Django REST Framework.AI Service Manager -> AI Providers.DeepSeek: HTTPS API Request
Backend Server.Django REST Framework.AI Service Manager -> AI Providers.Gemini: HTTPS API Request
Backend Server.Django REST Framework.AI Service Manager -> AI Providers.Ollama: HTTP API Request
